          "notes": [],
          "synonyms": []
        },
        {
          "sn": "4.",
          "fields": [
            "(Cookery)"
          ],
          "defs": [
            "To cover (a donut, cupcake, meat, etc.) with a thin layer of edible syrup, or other substance which may solidify to a glossy coating. The material used for glazing is usually sweet or highly flavored."
